- Plan Tier-1: codex BLOCK (verified-true: relative `specDir` makes EvalSymlinks/Rel falsely reject legit inside symlinks) → design amended with the filepath.Abs base + a relative-spec regression test; Opus GO; gemini GO (gemini actually noticed the Rel-mismatch but rationalized it as a safe failure — the class-#2 pattern again).
- Implement Tier-1: codex GO + Opus GO (adversarial probe clean) + gemini BLOCK (the missing-file diagnostic masking — verified-true, zero-downside fix) → distinguished os.ErrNotExist; gemini round-2 GO → UNANIMOUS.
